message.body: Bpp was good, great movement & good fluid. Will see ob on Friday @ 12:30.
Rockin! Thanks for the update. All is perfect. Everything will happen just when it needs to. How are you feeling?
Oh, est weight is 8lb3oz :) Feeling good, walked back home from appt (near Mt sinai), feels great to move tho humidity is sure gross!
I hear you. Let's be glad you won't be pregnant anymore once the intense heat sets in! Glad you're out and about. Keep hydrating, so important.
I think something's up... pink on tp & feeling crampy enough to not sleep at 3. now actual contractions I think, can time the feeling at least.
Talked to Dr #####, she said to call her around 7 unless I feel like I want to go in before then. They may like to eval me themselves at Mt Sinai at 830-9 before they go to their dowtown office.
